    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Portions of the foundations of some structures which transmit loads directly to the soil; used to distribute the weight of the superstructure over a greater area to prevent or reduce settlings.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
